.
.

Growing up, I didn’t see women who looked like me or had a similar background to me on the cover of any magazines, let alone the beauty magazines. I didn't have any role models to look up to who resembled me. Perhaps this is why I had a hard time thinking of myself as beautiful for a long time. I love that today the world is embracing the fact that all women are beautiful. If I could tell my younger self something it would be: you matter, your story matters, and you are beautiful. #DREAMBIG 
.

Rest in Peace @anguscloud 

Today, we gather to pay our deepest respects to the memory of Angus Cloud. It was truly an honor to have had the opportunity to work alongside him on the Puma Forever campaign. 

Angus was a remarkably talented actor, captivating audiences with his raw and authentic performances. His ability to immerse himself in every role he took on was extraordinary. Through his work, he showcased a range of emotions and brought characters to life in a way that few could. 

To the fans around the world who were touched by Angus' performances, we stand united in our sadness. His unique ability to connect with audiences through his work will forever be cherished.
